<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/experiment-log-914/offset/3">&lt;- Notice: Continued from 04XX.</a></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Show&nbsp;050X&nbsp;Test&nbsp;Logs</a></div>
